---
// src/components/drafting/DraftingFaqSection.astro
import { Plus } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- FAQ Items -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              What types of 2D drafting and design services do you provide?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We provide comprehensive 2D drafting services including architectural drawings, mechanical drafting, electrical schematics, structural drawings, and product design documentation. Our services cover floor plans, elevations, sections, construction details, assembly drawings, and technical illustrations with professional CAD standards and precise dimensioning.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              What CAD software and drawing standards do you use?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use industry-standard CAD software including AutoCAD, DraftSight, and other professional 2D drafting platforms. Our drawings follow AIA, NCS, and ISO standards with proper layer management, annotation styles, and drawing conventions. All deliverables are provided in standard formats including DWG, DXF, and PDF.
              <br /><br />
              Our comprehensive approach ensures complete technical documentation covering every aspect of your project for effective construction and manufacturing implementation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              How accurate and precise are your technical drawings?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our 2D drawings achieve Â±0.1mm precision accuracy using professional drafting techniques, precise dimensioning, and rigorous quality control processes. We employ multi-level verification including geometric accuracy checks, dimensional validation, and technical review to ensure the highest level of drawing precision and technical integrity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              Do you provide drawings for regulatory approval and permits?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes, we prepare drawings specifically for regulatory approval, building permits, and code compliance. Our drawings include all required information, proper title blocks, professional seals when applicable, and compliance with local building codes and industry standards for successful permit approval and regulatory review.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              How long does the 2D drafting process take?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Typical drafting projects follow a 3-4 week timeline: Week 1 for design analysis and planning, Week 2 for CAD development and drawing creation, Week 3 for quality review and verification, and Week 4 for final delivery.
              <br /><br />
              Timeline may vary based on project complexity, drawing quantity, and specific requirements. We provide detailed project schedules and regular progress updates throughout the drafting process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 6 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              Can you work from sketches, concepts, or existing drawings?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes, we can create professional CAD drawings from various sources including hand sketches, concept drawings, existing paper drawings, photographs, or rough CAD files. Our team can interpret and develop these into complete technical drawings with proper dimensioning, annotations, and professional formatting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- FAQ 7 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors duration-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
              Do you provide revisions and ongoing drawing support?
            </h3>
            <Plus size={20} className="text-slate-600 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" />
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content px-6 pb-4">
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We provide comprehensive post-delivery support including drawing revisions, format updates, and modifications for design changes. Our team maintains project files and can provide ongoing drafting services as your project evolves, ensuring continued accuracy and compliance with updated requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-16">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center text-white shadow-xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Need Professional 2D Drafting & Design Services?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-cyan-100 mb-6">
            Our experts are ready to create precise technical drawings that meet your project requirements and industry standards
          </p>
          <a href="/contact?#contact-form" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-white text-cyan-600 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
            Start Your Project
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqToggles = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle');
    
    faqToggles.forEach(toggle => {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', function(this: HTMLElement) {
        const content = this.nextElementSibling as HTMLElement;
        const icon = this.querySelector('svg') as SVGElement;
        
        if (content.style.display === 'none') {
          content.style.display = 'block';
          icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        } else {
          content.style.display = 'none';
          icon.style.transform = 'rotate(45deg)';
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          Get answers to common questions about 2D drafting and design services and our professional technical drawing process
        </p>
      </div>